%F A265272 The constant z satisfies:
%F A265272 (1) 2*z - 1/2 = Sum_{n>=1} [n*z] / 2^n,
%F A265272 (2) 2*z - 1/2 = Sum_{n>=1} 1 / 2^[n/z],
%F A265272 (3) 3/2 - 2*z = Sum_{n>=1} 1 / 2^[n/(1-z)],
%F A265272 (4) 3/2 - 2*z = Sum_{n>=1} [n*(1-z)] / 2^n,
%F A265272 (5) 1/2 = Sum_{n>=1} {n*(1-z)} / 2^n,
